<lb ed="I" n="0086b00" type="honorific"/><cb:mulu level="2" type="其他">本文</cb:mulu><head>本文</head>
<lb ed="I" n="0086b01" type="honorific"/><p xml:id="pI01p0086b0101">中岳嵩陽寺碑銘序
<lb ed="I" n="0086b02" type="honorific"/>夫至理空淨。非大智無以寄其言。法身凝<note n="0086001" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">𡧘＝寂【史】</note><note n="0086001" resp="ihp" type="mod">𡧘【佛拓】，寂【史】</note><app n="0086001"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">寂</lem><rdg wit="【原】">𡧘</rdg></app>。非妙信無以感其像。故託金
<lb ed="I" n="0086b03" type="honorific"/>軀於至敬之國。布慈雲於多士之世。顯皮紙骨筆之重。半偈亡身之貴。是
<lb ed="I" n="0086b04" type="honorific"/>以須達崇<note n="0086002" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">𦎍＝善【史】</note><note n="0086002" resp="ihp" type="mod">𦎍【佛拓】，善【史】</note><app n="0086002"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">善</lem><rdg wit="【原】">𦎍</rdg></app>。填金弗<note n="0086003" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30588"/>＝吝【史】</note><note n="0086003" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB30588"/>【佛拓】，吝【史】</note><app n="0086003"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">吝</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30588"/></rdg></app>。優王仰戀。鐫檀寫真。斯皆聖人留軌。為物樹業故
<lb ed="I" n="0086b05" type="honorific"/>然。乃遺形八万。還昇慧頂。有大德沙門生禪師。遊三空以歸真。<note n="0086004" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30589"/>＝汎【史】</note><note n="0086004" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB30589"/>【佛拓】，汎【史】</note><app n="0086004"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">汎</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30589"/></rdg></app>法流而
<lb ed="I" n="0086b06" type="honorific"/>御世。控三車而徽蹤。秉常樂以係軌。隱顯無方。沉浮崧嶺。道風遠被。德香
<lb ed="I" n="0086b07" type="honorific"/>普薰。乃皇帝傾心以師資。朝野望風而屈<note n="0086005" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30590"/>＝膝【史】</note><note n="0086005" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB30590"/>【佛拓】，膝【史】</note><app n="0086005"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">膝</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30590"/></rdg></app>。<note n="0086006" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">𣥖＝此【史】</note><note n="0086006" resp="ihp" type="mod">𣥖【佛拓】，此【史】</note><app n="0086006"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">此</lem><rdg wit="【原】">𣥖</rdg></app>山先來未有塔廟。禪師將
<lb ed="I" n="0086b08" type="honorific"/>欲接引四生。永<note n="0086007" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">辤＝辭【史】</note><note n="0086007" resp="ihp" type="mod">辤【佛拓】，辭【史】</note><app n="0086007"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">辭</lem><rdg wit="【原】">辤</rdg></app>沸鑊。<note n="0086008" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30591"/>＝拯【史】</note><note n="0086008" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB30591"/>【佛拓】，拯【史】</note><app n="0086008"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">拯</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30591"/></rdg></app>拔群品。遠離炎鑪。卜茲福<note n="0086009" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30592"/>＝地【史】</note><note n="0086009" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB30592"/>【佛拓】，地【史】</note><app n="0086009"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">地</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30592"/></rdg></app>。創立神場。當中岳
<lb ed="I" n="0086b09" type="honorific"/>之要害。對眾術之摳<note n="0086010" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30593"/>＝牙【史】</note><note n="0086010" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB30593"/>【佛拓】，牙【史】</note><app n="0086010"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">牙</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30593"/></rdg></app>。乃北背高峰。南臨廣陌。西帶濬澗。<note n="0086011" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">柬＝東【史】</note><note n="0086011" resp="ihp" type="mod">柬【佛拓】，東【史】</note><app n="0086011"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">東</lem><rdg wit="【原】">柬</rdg></app>接脩林。於太
<lb ed="I" n="0086b10" type="honorific"/>和八年。歲次甲子。建造伽藍。築立塔<note n="0086012" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30594"/>＝殿【史】</note><note n="0086012" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB30594"/>【佛拓】，殿【史】</note><app n="0086012"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">殿</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30594"/></rdg></app>。布置僧坊。略深梗概。公王卿士。咸
<lb ed="I" n="0086b11" type="honorific"/>發<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">布</unclear>向之心。凡厥庶民。並欣喜捨之志。司空公裴衍。昔在齊都。欽承師德。
<lb ed="I" n="0086b12" type="honorific"/>願歸中國。為寺檀主。本願既從。雲歸<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">表</unclear>節。禪師乃構千善靈塔一十五層。
<lb ed="I" n="0086b13" type="honorific"/>始就七級。緣<note n="0086013" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">荖＝差【史】</note><note n="0086013" resp="ihp" type="mod">荖【佛拓】，差【史】</note><app n="0086013"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">差</lem><rdg wit="【原】">荖</rdg></app>中止。而七層之狀。遠望則迢亭魏峨。仰參天漢。近視則□
<lb ed="I" n="0086b14" type="honorific"/>嵬儼嶷。旁魄絕望。自佛法光興。未有斯壯也。禪師指麾。成之匪日。禪師<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">背</unclear>
<lb ed="I" n="0086b15" type="honorific"/>後。雖復名工巧匠。無<note n="0086014" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30595"/>＝能【史】</note><note n="0086014" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB30595"/>【佛拓】，能【史】</note><app n="0086014"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">能</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30595"/></rdg></app>陟其嶮峭。禪師大弟子沙門統倫。艷。二法師。並妙
<lb ed="I" n="0086b16" type="honorific"/>　　　　　　　　　思淵賾。神<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">智</unclear>難量。繼軌四依。津道<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">緣</unclear>世。覺華散藻。
<lb ed="I" n="0086b17" type="honorific"/>　　　　　　　　　戒<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">香</unclear><note n="0086015" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30596"/>＝氛【史】</note><note n="0086015" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB30596"/>【佛拓】，氛【史】</note><app n="0086015"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">氛</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30596"/></rdg></app>馥。<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">與</unclear>諸同志。以師遺功。成茲洪業。分<note n="0086016" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30597"/>＝稟【史】</note><note n="0086016" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB30597"/>【佛拓】，稟【史】</note><app n="0086016"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">稟</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30597"/></rdg></app><unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">餘</unclear>
<lb ed="I" n="0086b18" type="honorific"/>　　　　　　　　　塼。更<note n="0086017" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30598"/>＝罩【史】</note><note n="0086017" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB30598"/>【佛拓】，罩【史】</note><app n="0086017"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">罩</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30598"/></rdg></app>兩塔。<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">並</unclear>各七層。仰副師願。殊特妙巧。□創
<lb ed="I" n="0086b19" type="honorific"/>　　　　　　　　　秀出。塔<app type="star" corresp="#0086012"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">殿</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30594"/></rdg></app>宮堂。星羅<note n="0086018" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">棊＝棋【史】</note><note n="0086018" resp="ihp" type="mod">棊【佛拓】，棋【史】</note><app n="0086018"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">棋</lem><rdg wit="【原】">棊</rdg></app>布。內外圖寫本生。<note n="0086019" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">埿＝泥【史】</note><note n="0086019" resp="ihp" type="mod">埿【佛拓】，泥【史】</note><app n="0086019"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">泥</lem><rdg wit="【原】">埿</rdg></app>曰。十
<lb ed="I" n="0086b20" type="honorific"/>　　　　　　　　　方尊儀。無量億<note n="0086020" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30599"/>＝數【史】</note><note n="0086020" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB30599"/>【佛拓】，數【史】</note><app n="0086020"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">數</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30599"/></rdg></app>。或<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">鑄</unclear>金為相。裁玉成豪。瓖碧煜
<lb ed="I" n="0086b21" type="honorific"/>　　　　　　　　　爍。丹彩絢燿。色煥□□。光煇宇宙。異類眾多。罔知
<lb ed="I" n="0086b22" type="honorific"/>　　　　　　　　　厝緒。龕房禪室。側□環遶。逕閣通門。前後<note n="0086021" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30388"/>＝樓【史】</note><note n="0086021" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB30388"/>【佛拓】，樓【史】</note><app n="0086021"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">樓</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30388"/></rdg></app>□。墻
<lb ed="I" n="0086b23" type="honorific"/>　　　　　　　　　廊重複。菀衍逶迤。<note n="0086022" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">𩑬＝規【史】</note><note n="0086022" resp="ihp" type="mod">𩑬【佛拓】，規【史】</note><app n="0086022"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">規</lem><rdg wit="【原】">𩑬</rdg></app>而有楷。短而有則。溝霤雙泉。
<lb ed="I" n="0086b24" type="honorific"/>四殖甘菓。柳裊長條。松擎圓蓋。池荷炤灼。翠葉紅輝。微波碧澈。潺流灒瀨。
<lb ed="I" n="0086b25" type="honorific"/>異禽巡獸。飲喙相鳴。碩學名賢。踵武相望。引房清誦。列館法言。洪鍾一扣。
<lb ed="I" n="0086b26" type="honorific"/>應真四集。唄響八飛。香煙似霧。虔禮禪<app type="star" corresp="#0086001"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">寂</lem><rdg wit="【原】">𡧘</rdg></app>。六時靡輟。方為眾聖万劫之靈
<lb ed="I" n="0086b27" type="honorific"/>場。八輩十方三世之菀囿也。天平二年四月八日。倫。艷二統。乃<note n="0086023" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30600"/>＝刊【史】</note><note n="0086023" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB30600"/>【佛拓】，刊【史】</note><app n="0086023"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">刊</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30600"/></rdg></app>石樹碑。
<lb ed="I" n="0086b28" type="honorific"/>雕飾尊像。贊貽嘉福。顯彰聖儀。高足大沙門統遵法師。忘懷體道。戒珠<note n="0086024" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">晈＝皎【史】</note><note n="0086024" resp="ihp" type="mod">晈【佛拓】，皎【史】</note><app n="0086024"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">皎</lem><rdg wit="【原】">晈</rdg></app>
<lb ed="I" n="0086b29" type="honorific"/>潔。仁智<note n="0086025" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">朙＝明【史】</note><note n="0086025" resp="ihp" type="mod">朙【佛拓】，明【史】</note><app n="0086025"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">明</lem><rdg wit="【原】">朙</rdg></app>敏。器宇汪庠。開妙思於三空之表。顯真如於四忍之外。接引群
<lb ed="I" n="0086b30" type="honorific"/>生。舟航巨海。率諸邑義。繕立天宮。<note n="0086026" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">𠢫＝整【史】</note><note n="0086026" resp="ihp" type="mod">𠢫【佛拓】，整【史】</note><app n="0086026"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">整</lem><rdg wit="【原】">𠢫</rdg></app>脩嚴麗。兼造白玉像一龕。眷屬侍御。
<lb ed="I" n="0086b31" type="honorific"/>剞劂鐫磨。妙匠精巧。三十二滿。八十好圓。色揜耀靈。光暉夜兔。以諸勝<app type="star" corresp="#0086002"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">善</lem><rdg wit="【原】">𦎍</rdg></app>。
<lb ed="I" n="0086b32" type="honorific"/>仰資皇帝。聖曆無窮。國境寧泰。太后德被蒼海。永保仁齡。預捨一豪。同登
<lb ed="I" n="0086b33" type="honorific"/>我淨。若見若聞。等一常樂。傍盡<note n="0086027" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">𨕙＝邊【史】</note><note n="0086027" resp="ihp" type="mod">𨕙【佛拓】，邊【史】</note><app n="0086027"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">邊</lem><rdg wit="【原】">𨕙</rdg></app>塵。後窮來際。咸鍾<app type="star" corresp="#0086006"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">此</lem><rdg wit="【原】">𣥖</rdg></app>福。其詞曰。
<lb ed="I" n="0086b34" type="honorific"/><app type="star" corresp="#0086025"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">明</lem><rdg wit="【原】">朙</rdg></app><app type="star" corresp="#0086025"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">明</lem><rdg wit="【原】">朙</rdg></app>大聖。<app type="star" corresp="#0086024"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">皎</lem><rdg wit="【原】">晈</rdg></app><app type="star" corresp="#0086024"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">皎</lem><rdg wit="【原】">晈</rdg></app>無著。至<app type="star" corresp="#0086001"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">寂</lem><rdg wit="【原】">𡧘</rdg></app>至妙。湛然常樂。無像無言。形名應世。七步舉手。
<lb ed="I" n="0086b35" type="honorific"/>播宣苦諦。聲光振動。濯我塵滯。化息雙林。終歸實際。金儀言寢。塔像勃興。
<lb ed="I" n="0086b36" type="honorific"/>香尊避坐。多寶踊昇。為摸為揩。永劫<note n="0086028" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30604"/>＝祇【史】</note><note n="0086028" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB30604"/>【佛拓】，祇【史】</note><app n="0086028"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">祇</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30604"/></rdg></app>承。維大沙門。權機應傳。英風秀朗。
<lb ed="I" n="0086b37" type="honorific"/>弘通常住。道德芳烈。帝后欽裕。搆造靈基。朝野傾務。遠摹妙喜。近光祇樹。
<lb ed="I" n="0086b38" type="honorific"/>唯聖唯賢。爰依爰附。億兆來蘇。天龍虔仰。城芥千空。<app type="star" corresp="#0086006"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">此</lem><rdg wit="【原】">𣥖</rdg></app>基無爽。</p>
